{
  "stem": "3040.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had a-- a large barrack where they did laundry for-- for the officers and for the-- the guards and everybody, and they put me to work there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then they put me to-- they took me out of this-- of this work detail, and they put me into a barracks where they had a-- they made handles to axes.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To axes, to ax.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] No.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Why don't-- don't I-- the, you know, wooden handles for ax.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Is it not axes?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's axes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, this is where I worked a few days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But there was a terrible, terrible supervisor, a German, who had-- he had to kill everybody.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Every day, he had to kill somebody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He, you know, he was walking around with these long handles and just hitting people for no reason until they-- they got-- they were dead.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said this-- I don't want to wind up dead that-- that way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So one day, I decided not to-- not to appear, not to go to work, not to appear in the morning.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How do you go to work in a concentration camp?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody's out of the barracks, assemble in a-- in a-- in a square in the center.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They call it the Appellplatz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from there, details went to different-- to different places in the-- in-- in the camp to work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Instead of going to the Appellplatz, I was hiding under the barracks, because I didn't want to go back to that place because I knew one day I'm going to wind up dead from that-- from-- from a beating.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one day, two days, you know, I-- I managed to escape-- to escape that.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
